    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered at $17,500, and that price honestly reflects its fair condition \u2014 it runs and drives dependably for daily use, but prospective buyers should be aware of its age and accumulated wear. The exterior shows visible scratches, minor dents, and some paint fading consistent with regular use over the years. Inside, the upholstery has worn spots and there are scuffs on various trim pieces. Mechanically, the engine starts reliably and the transmission shifts adequately, though we recommend a pre-purchase inspection as some components may be approaching the end of their service life. This is a practical, honest buy for someone who needs reliable transportation and isn't looking for a showroom-quality vehicle.",
