    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition, and we're committed to giving you an honest, complete picture before you buy. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 the paint retains a healthy shine with only minor surface blemishes consistent with normal everyday use, such as a few light scratches and small stone chips that are typical for a vehicle of this age. There are no dents or structural damage to report. The interior is clean and comfortable, showing moderate wear on the seating surfaces and controls, but nothing that detracts significantly from the driving experience. Mechanically, the vehicle runs reliably \u2014 the engine starts smoothly, the transmission shifts without hesitation, and all major systems are functioning as expected. We do recommend a pre-purchase inspection, as we believe in full transparency. This is a solid, dependable vehicle that will serve its next owner well, priced fairly to reflect its genuine good condition.",
